	<td bgcolor="#DEDFDF" width="100%" valign="top">
	<font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial"> <b></b></font>
	<p><font size="2" face="Verdana, Arial">WOOHOOO!!!!! I so wanted to be a melee class! THANX!<br />
<br />
My favorite part:<br />
<br />
<blockquote><font size="1" face="Verdana, Arial">quote:</font><hr>"I really want to invite a cleric because they can do X, and that will be really helpful."<hr></blockquote><br />
<br />
So what is "X"? Melee? Heal? Both? Are VI people stupider than I think? Clerics all over Norrath I'm sure are chomping at the bit to bag their epics and blackstars, put away thier lanterns, waste a spell gem for Yaulp 5 and melee with their NEW UBER SUMMONED WEAPON!<br />
<br />
Notice folks, that there is no mention of increased offense or 1hb skills. No mention of increased defense. No double hit. No nothing. I have over 1250AC and 3800HP with full buffs, and I still get pwned like a red headed step child in most zones that give me experience.<br />
<br />
Now, don't get me completely wrong. I don't necessarily think that clerics becoming more melee oriented is necessarily a bad thing. D&D clerics of old used to do some pretty fair melee damage, and I'll be the first to admit that melee is fun on occasion (and yes I do it now).<br />
<br />
However. If they are going to go this route, they need to go FURTHER.<br />
<br />
#1. INCREASE OFFENSIVE, DEFENSIVE, 1HB, AND 2HB CAPS!!!!!<br />
#2. Make better ratio cleric weaps.<br />
#3. Up proc rate on current good procing damage cleric weaps (Dawnfire, Truesight Hammer... I don't want to use the stupid summoned weap all the time)<br />
#4. Yaulp 5 better stack with BAoTR!<br />
<br />
Personally... I think VI is stupid, If i wanted to play a gimp melee class, i would have picked -insertgimpmeleeclasshere-. If PoP is gonna be that hard that you have to give better heals to other classes. Problem easily solved. <br />
<br />
Give Druids the freaking 1600 heal for 550mana... it better fits their line anyway. Add a snare effect to the group CE spell and give it to shamans for 800mana or so. Don't give druids a near-CH quality spell.  Give a near CH-quality spell to clerics for an 8sec cast and 300mana.  I would be happy with these changes. They wouldn't FORCE ME TO BECOME A MELEE CLASS TO GET AN EXP GROUP.  VI is going about this completely the wrong way.  Dont make druids a non-melee cleric equivelent.  Make Clerics BETTER and MORE EFFICIENT, while making OTHER HEALERS BETTER AND MORE EFFICIENT!<br />
<br />
I'm just completely shocked at this. Shocked actually isnt the best word. Amazed... flabergasted...<br />
<br />
PS. WTB a CoF<br />
<br />
-Moka 60 CLR</font></p>
	
